{
  "text": "To compare the newly developed equation with current regression models, we also estimated METs from the regression equations of Freedson et al. (7), Hendelman et al. [CITATION_1] , and Swartz et al. [CITATION_2] . A one-way repeated-measures ANOVA was used to compare actual and predicted METs for each activity using the cross-validation group. In addition, a one-way repeated-measures ANOVA was used to compare actual and predicted METs for all 18 activities combined. Pairwise comparisons with Bonferroni adjustments were performed to locate significant differences when necessary.",
  "correct_citation": {
